Basic:
1-B, 2-B, 3-B, 4-B, 5-C, 6-B, 7-B, 8-C, 9-B, 10-C

Intermediate:
11-B, 12-B, 13-B, 14-B, 15-B, 16-A, 17-C, 18-B, 19-B, 20-A

Advanced:
21-B, 22-B, 23-B, 24-B, 25-B, 26-B, 27-C, 28-B, 29-C, 30-B

